data.title: Revealing the global longline fleet with satellite radar | Scientific Reports
data.description: Because many vessels use the Automatic Identification System (AIS) to broadcast GPS positions, recent advances in satellite technology have enabled us to map global fishing activity. Understanding of human activity at sea, however, is limited because an unknown number of vessels do not broadcast AIS. Those vessels can be detected by satellite-based Synthetic Aperture Radar (SAR) imagery, but this technology has not yet been deployed at scale to estimate the size of fleets in the open ocean. Here we combine SAR and AIS for large-scale open ocean monitoring, developing methods to match vessels with AIS to vessels detected with SAR and estimate the number of non-broadcasting vessels. We reveal that, between September 2019 and January 2020, non-broadcasting vessels accounted for about 35% of the longline activity north of Madagascar and 10% of activity near French Polynesia and Kiribati's Line Islands. We further demonstrate that this method could monitor half of the global longline activity with about 70 SAR images per week, allowing us to track human activity across the oceans.

data.title: Amy Winter Thermal Phone Pocket Tech Leggings | Lorna Jane
data.description: Introducing Cosmopolitan's #1 Rated Thermal Legging, and your new go-to winter legging with the perfect balance of tech and fashion. The soft brushed lining traps your body heat to keep you warm and the higher rise waist provides support and additional coverage to keep the warmth in. The design lends its self to be easily dressed up or dressed down for ultimate styling versatility. Plus it has not one but two phone pockets for hands free life on the go. Our Amy Winter Thermal Phone Pocket Tech legging has also been designed with a gusset. This triangular panel of fabric sewn into the crotch (gusset) prevents the leggings from 'riding up' (no camel toe) and provides more flexibility and freedom of movement. The thermal lining also gives a more compressive feel when worn. If you would prefer a more relaxed fit for all day wear we suggest you go up a size. If you prefer a more snug and firm fit, we suggest your usual size. PLEASE NOTE: Due to the nature of brushed fleece, these leggings can be prone to pilling so we recommend washing yours inside out in our Active Washbag on a delicate cycle to extend it's life. If you do not own a garment bag, a gentle hand wash is recommended.
